description: Style and sophistication join forces in this classic brick and beam residence with an open concept kitchen featuring modern cabinetry, stone counters, and stainless steel appliances.  High ceilings and oversized windows accentuate the industrial style this home exudes.  Plenty of space for a sectional or sofa/loveseat combo, and a dining table too. The beautiful wood beamed ceilings bring a calming natural feel to the space. Lots of upgrades in this unit too including newer appliance package, and totally new HVAC system (over $20,000). Great en-suite bedroom too with walk-in closet! In unit washer/dryer. Deeded garage parking too! Court Square Press is a full service luxury condominium featuring 24/7 concierge, on-site fitness facility, beautiful common areas including a central courtyard, and a 15,000 sq ft roof top pool terrace with BBQ's, and views of the city skyline.  Located in one of Boston's hottest neighborhoods with award winning restaurants, The T, Starbucks and more!
